              <li tabindex="-1" style="width: 254.76000000000002px; max-width: none; min-width: auto;" data-item-index="1" id="ember227" class="artdeco-carousel__item ember-view"><div data-test-display="display" class="artdeco-carousel__item-container">
    
                
          <div class="artdeco-card pv-profile-component-builder__card full-width display-flex flex-column">
            
    <div class="display-flex flex-column full-width
        full-height
        
        ">
      
        <a class="optional-action-target-wrapper" target="_self" tabindex="-1" href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7060876311291998208?updateEntityUrn=urn%3Ali%3Afs_feedUpdate%3A%28V2%2Curn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7060876311291998208%29">
        <div class="pvs-content__top-bar">
            <div class="mt3 mb2 mh3 display-flex t-12 t-black--light display-flex t-normal">
              <span aria-hidden="true"><!---->Post<!----></span><span class="visually-hidden"><!---->Post<!----></span>
            </div>
        </div>
          
    <div class="display-flex ">
      
      <div class="
          display-flex full-width">
        
          
      <div class="qjszbQThRDmTuIGmbqIzvODBkRwShlwAuGw
          full-width t-14 t-normal t-black ph3
              pb2
              text-body-small display-flex align-items-center" dir="ltr">
        
    <div class="tCUdawTWbPWpyaHvhYhjeArwvkfHgpUM
        inline-show-more-text--is-collapsed
        inline-show-more-text--is-collapsed-with-line-clamp
        
        text-align-left
        
         full-width" style="-webkit-line-clamp:2;" dir="ltr" tabindex="-1">

        <span dir="ltr"><!---->What an incredible event! I can't help but share my top 5 key takeaways from the conference, which are essential for professionals in the industry. 🚀<!----><br><br><!---->1️⃣ The importance of an audited and rehearsed IRP (Incident Response Plan) involving the IRT (Incident Response Team) cannot be overstated. Audit your plan today and rehearse it this month, as little thinking during the actual incident is crucial for accurate<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23results&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>results</span></a><!---->.<!----><br><!---->2️⃣ I heard it directly from one of the CISO's I met: "as a<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23ciso&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>CISO</span></a><!---->, my primary goal is to stay out of the newspaper". CISOs already have sleepless nights - that won't change, so, as vendors, let's help them avoid unwanted headlines. Do you agree or disagree? Share your thoughts!<!----><br><!---->3️⃣<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23ai&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>AI</span></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span>is transforming the landscape for both defenders and attackers. While it empowers and augments human defenders, attackers have direct access to these advanced capabilities too. And I'm afraid attackers will always be more sophisticated in exploiting AI's capabilities to create significantly more evasive attacks.<!----><br><!---->4️⃣ Developers face significant cyber-risks from third-party tools, plugins, and dependencies. Protecting developers as a market is challenging, and is a<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23blueocean&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>BlueOcean</span></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span>for vendors.<!----><br><!---->5️⃣ Get familiar with the concept: "Left of Boom -&gt; Boom -&gt; Right of Boom". It's incredibly practical and helpful for both strategic and tactical discussions and execution. Stay tuned for a future post elaborating on this concept! (Thanks,<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><a tabindex="0" href="/in/irawinkler/" id="ember231" class="ember-view"><!---->Ira Winkler<!----></a><!---->,<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><a tabindex="0" href="/in/drtcbrown/" id="ember232" class="ember-view"><!---->Tracy Celaya<!----></a><!---->,<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><a tabindex="0" href="/in/adriana-winkler/" id="ember233" class="ember-view"><!---->Adriana A.<!----></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span>for sharing this in a practical session, that wasn't recorded). For now I'll just say - Left of Boom<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23prevention&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>prevention</span></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span>is key - invest in the best prevention you can afford.<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><br><span class="white-space-pre"> </span><!----><!----><br><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " target="_self" tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/one-rsac/" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span><!---->RSAC<!----></span></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span>2023 was truly insightful and a must-attend for professionals - many of whom I met and will mention in future posts. What's your take on these key points? How can we continue to push the boundaries and stay ahead in the industry? 💡<!----><br><span class="white-space-pre"> </span><!----><!----><br><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA "         text-align-left
        
         full-width" style="-webkit-line-clamp:2;" dir="ltr" tabindex="-1">

        <span dir="ltr"><!---->"Please find the mistake in that sentence" is an instruction every schoolkid hears.<!----><br><br><!---->We often carry forward<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23habits&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>habits</span></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span>from our school days that don't serve us well in our family and professional lives. One such habit is the relentless pursuit of finding<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23mistakes&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>mistakes</span></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span>in others' work. While this may have served us in our academic journey, it can often lead to a<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23judgmental&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>judgmental</span></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span>attitude, which is detrimental to connecting with others.<!----><br><br><!---->People don't like being judged, they crave<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23connection&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>connection</span></a><!---->.<!----><br><br><!---->How?<!----><br><!---->As an adult, and especially as a leader, prepare with an intention for each daily connection. What would I like to happen? What type of connection would I like to form here?<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><br><br><!---->This approach fosters a collaborative environment, boosts engagement, and drives success. 🚀<!----><br><!---->Don't focus on the mistake, focus on the action, the connection, and the<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23result&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>result</span></a><!---->.&nbsp;🎯<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><br><br><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23leadershipdevelopment&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>LeadershipDevelopment</span></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span><!----><!----><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23teambuilding&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>TeamBuilding</span></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span><!----><!----><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23professionalgrowth&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>ProfessionalGrowth</span></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span><!----><!----></span>

<!---->    </div>
  
      </div>

          tvm-parent-container">
<!---->        <span dir="ltr"><!---->The picture: my very first AI generated package!<!----><span><br></span><span><br></span><!---->Yesterday, something remarkable happened: my first-ever AI package arrived, fully prepared by a ChatGPT Agent!<!----><span><br></span><span><br></span><!---->I asked the Agent to identify the best products tailored specifically for me - based on my personal preferences and even my blood test results.<span class="white-space-pre"> </span><span><br></span><!---->It carefully curated a selection of nuts, seeds, and dried fruits that perfectly matched my health profile (iron, omega-3, magnesium etc.), picking only the very best options without me needing to spend the time.<!----><span><br></span><span><br></span><!---->The Agent navigated an actual grocery website, tackled product quantities, minimum order rules, and edge cases in real-time.<!----><span><br></span><span><br></span><!---->The result? An automatic basket filled with 17 healthy products, arriving smoothly at my doorstep the very next day.<!----><span><br></span><span><br></span><!---->Three exciting insights:<!----><span><br></span><!---->1. This technology will become seamless in just a few iterations.<!----><span><br></span><!---->2. E-commerce sites not optimized for AI-driven agents risk falling behind.<!----><span><br></span><!---->3. Weekly grocery shopping as a manual chore? Soon to be history.<!----><span><br></span><span><br></span><!---->Thrilled to see AI leap from experiment to everyday reality!<!----><span><br></span><span><br></span><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23chatgpt&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>ChatGPT</span></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span><!----><!----><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23agent&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>Agent</span></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span><!----><!----><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23openai&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>OpenAI</span></a><span class="white-space-pre"> </span><!----><!----><a class="EaWzLdfjwgloMRCqeXHrsnLLcqdpxKtzA " tabindex="0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23grocery&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" data-test-app-aware-link=""><span class="visually-hidden">hashtag</span><span><span aria-hidden="true">#</span>Grocery</span></a></span>

Delivered groundbreaking security solutions that redefined how organizations protect their most sensitive assets.

Key Achievements:

* Led the design and development of KAZUAR’s flagship product from ideation to sales - a secure and scalable platform that protects data and privacy across multiple devices and networks. I guided the product from a concept to a solution that customers use and value.
* Worked on building partnerships to strengthen KAZUAR's unique value proposition while protecting the company’s intellectual property.
* Focused on creating value by improving product leadership and making sure products met the needs of both current and future customers.

Core Areas of Focus:

1. Strategic Execution: Delivered projects and initiatives in line with KAZUAR's roadmap, ensuring the company met its goals while adapting to changes in the market.
2. Innovation and IP Protection: Encouraged new ideas and ensured key technologies were protected through intellectual property rights.
3. Partnerships and Expertise: Collaborated with industry leaders to develop advanced solutions and strengthen KAZUAR’s position in the cybersecurity market.
4. Customer-Centric Solutions: Applied new technologies to improve the company’s offerings and ensure they met the needs of a changing market.

Throughout my time at KAZUAR, I focused on integrating new technologies and ensuring that our technical efforts supported the company’s long-term goals and customer expectations.<!----></span>

         full-width" style="-webkit-line-clamp:2;" dir="ltr" tabindex="-1">

        <span aria-hidden="true"><!---->Computerized methods and systems receive neutralized data items on a first entity from a second entity over a network by receiving a first data item from the second entity. A security protocol that applies rules and policies is applied to the first data item to create a second data item that is a neutralized version of the first data item. The first data item and the second data item are converted into comparable forms. The second data item is analyzed against the first data item by comparing the comparable forms to form at least one comparison measure. The second data item is received on the endpoint if the at least one comparison measure satisfies a threshold criterion. The security protocol is modified to adjust the applied rules and policies if the at least one comparison measure does not satisfy the threshold criterion.<!----></span><span class="visually-hidden"><!---->Computerized methods and systems receive neutralized data items on a first entity from a second entity over a network by receiving a first data item from the second entity. A security protocol that applies rules and policies is applied to the first data item to create a second data item that is a neutralized version of the first data item. The first data item and the second data item are converted into comparable forms. The second data item is analyzed against the first data item by comparing the comparable forms to form at least one comparison measure. The second data item is received on the endpoint if the at least one comparison measure satisfies a threshold criterion. The security protocol is modified to adjust the applied rules and policies if the at least one comparison measure does not satisfy the threshold criterion.<!----></span>

איתור קהל יעד מדויק לפי תפקיד, תחום, גאוגרפיה ותחומי עניין

ניסוח הודעות אישיות וממוקדות שמייצרות מעורבות

השירות יעיל במיוחד עבור:
חברות שמחפשות לקוחות חדשים ומעוניינות להרחיב את פעילותן

סטארטאפים שמבקשים לגייס משקיעים או לאמת נחיצות של מוצר\שירות

הזמנה לכנסים\וובינארים

אם הנושא רלוונטי אשמח לשוחח עמך.


עופר
